notes: Supersub - Each team can now designate a 12th man (Supersub) who will be able to bat or bowl. The change will be announced over the PA system and details of the change shown on the giant screen.

milestones.description: Fleming and Lou Vincent's 204-run partnership is NZ's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 193 between Fleming and Nathan Astle
Lou Vincent has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (118) in an innings in ODIs for NZ, going past Nathan Astle's 88
Lou Vincent's 172 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for NZ), surpassing Glenn Turner's 171
Andy Blignaut has conceded the most runs in an innings (96) in ODIs for ZIM, going past Panyangara's record of 86
Lou Vincent has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (9) in ODIs for NZ, going past Chris Cairns's 7
This is the highest match aggregate (602) involving teams New Zealand & Zimbabwe in ODIs
Fleming and Lou Vincent's 204-run partnership is NZ's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 193 between Nathan Astle and Fleming
